snippet.title: AMBER HEARD'S DISRESPECTFUL AND RACIST TWEET ABOUT LANDSCAPERS
snippet.description:
Amber Heard slammed for warning nannies and landscapers about ICE checkpoint Amber Heard faced massive reactions on Twitter when she tried to warn neighbors of a US immigration and customs checkpoint. UU Near your house.

"I just heard that there is an ICE checkpoint in Hollywood, a few blocks from where I live in. It is better that everyone give their housewives, nannies and landscapers a ride home tonight ..." he wrote in an since-deleted tweet.

Twitter users were quick to call her.

damn amber, you think this sounds awoke, huh, "tweeted a user.

"Hi, amber, I love you so much that I'm going to tell you this: not all immigrants are housewives, nannies and landscapers (not that there is anything wrong with being), but this stereotype should have been eradicated some time ago," he said. other.

Heard did not apologize for his original tweet, but followed up with another on the immigration checkpoints.

"Checkpoints in their home streets .... Is this the" great "United States we're targeting? Raids, fences and police state controls do not feel like the 'land of the free' they built our immigrant ancestors. "
